-I lost interest. We win?

34:38.117 --> 34:40.119
We did, actually. The jury found for us.

34:40.203 --> 34:42.622
See, I told you.
Deep down, people hate the environment.

34:42.705 --> 34:45.208
That wasn't it, Denny, but you're welcome.

34:46.584 --> 34:47.460
Thank you.

34:47.543 --> 34:49.462
