to get Alzheimer's?

36:29.478 --> 36:31.439
I'll make it. You watch.

36:31.522 --> 36:35.318
What are the odds of somebody
getting mad cow and Alzheimer's?

36:35.401 --> 36:38.487
Right. (chuckles)

36:38.571 --> 36:40.656
See? Now I feel good.

36:41.449 --> 36:44.744
I think it's good to live life as though
it were a finite thing, 'cause it is.

36:46.037 --> 36:47.371
I appreciate today.

36:49.081 --> 36:54.503
And tomorrow, I'll wake up,
and there'll be another day to savor.

36:57.173 --> 37:00.009
And after it, I'll go to bed,
and I'll wake up, and there'll be another.

37:01.427 --> 37:03.596
Another and another and a...

37:07.433 --> 37:10.853
Besides, I can reverse this, uh,

37:11.562 --> 37:13.439
MCI thing anytime I want.

37:13.522 --> 37:15.858
-You can?
-DENNY: I-I read a study.

37:15.942 --> 37:18.402
Blood goes to your brain,
