37:24.367 --> 37:26.994
Question is, is it really worth it?

37:28.955 --> 37:31.249
-I think Plato once asked that.
-(Denny chuckles)

37:32.208 --> 37:34.293
Ah. (chuckles)

37:34.377 --> 37:36.671
Don't you love Christmas?

37:36.754 --> 37:38.798
(siren wailing in the distance)

37:39.298 --> 37:42.009
Anything goes wrong in the world,
Christmas makes it go away.

37:43.177 --> 37:46.597
Decorations, carols...

37:48.391 --> 37:49.225
tree.

