38:04.699 --> 38:08.703
And, um, Diana Korolog,
I think I've mentioned her to you.

38:08.786 --> 38:11.414
She brought her slutty cousin along,

38:11.497 --> 38:16.127
and-and she was
dressed so beautifully in uh...

38:16.460 --> 38:18.504
She had the popcorn strings around her,

38:18.587 --> 38:22.591
