38:48.993 --> 38:53.247
-Have you bought my present yet?
-Well, it's still a little early.

38:53.331 --> 38:56.125
-I know what I want.
-Tell me.

38:56.834 --> 39:00.921
Well, I saw you dancing close
with Lorraine.

39:01.005 --> 39:02.965
A lot closer than I'll ever get.

39:03.049 --> 39:04.550
But I've resigned myself to that.

39:05.551 --> 39:10.264
And her perfume rubbed off on you.
